					h3 Limiting use, disclosure and retention

					p We will use or disclose Your personal information only for the purposes for which it was collected, except with Your consent or as required or permitted by law. We will retain your personal information as long as necessary for the fulfilment of those purposes, subject to statutory or regulatory retention requirements and legitimate business reasons.
