					p We comply with Our obligations under the applicable Data protection regulation by:

					ul 
						li Keeping Personal data up to date;
						li Storing and destroying it securely;
						li Not collecting or retaining excessive amounts of data;
						li Protecting Personal data from loss, misuse, unauthorised access and disclosure and by ensuring that appropriate technical and organizational measures are in place to protect personal data.

